# Implementation Plan — Shared Pool Solana Program + Oracle Backend

## Goal

Replace the DuelDuck 1v1 duel model with a **custom parimutuel shared-pool prediction system** built on Solana. Users predict Over/Under on a specific stat (corners, goals, cards) at a specific minute. All stakes go into a shared on-chain pool. When the strike minute arrives, a backend oracle reads TxODDS live data and resolves the pool. Winners split the pot proportionally.

